body:
Hey @josh11b,
@skye mentioned that very same thing above. The whole point of my pull request is to allow you to open up that very same `name_scope` without having to carry around the `name_scope` object.
I myself find this useful because it allows me to group operations logically in tensorboard without blowing up my code by passing around `name_scope` objects.
